com.ecmdeveloper.eds.model

Interface Property


  • public interface Property
    The property interface. This interface is used to configure the behavior of a specific property. Once a property is modified, it has to be added to the ExternalDataResponse to be effective.
    Author:
    Ricardo Belfor
